OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775913059
OL,3,C'He wanted to finish me off. All I
OL,4,Cever wanted to do was love him' -
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FUTV can shed even more light on why
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland is the most dangerous
OL,9,Fplace in the UK to be a woman.
OL,11,FWe can exclusively reveal for every
OL,12,Fone of the 30 women murdered here in
OL,13,Fjust over five years there was a
OL,14,Ffailed attempt to kill three others.
OL,16,FIf those women had lost their lives
OL,17,Fpolice would have been investigating
OL,18,F121 femicides.
OL,20,FPolice mounted 91 attempted murder
OL,21,Finvestigations.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
