PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775913059
OL,3,C'He wanted to finish me off. All I
OL,4,Cever wanted to do was love him' -
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FSuperintendent Kerry Brennan told us:
OL,8,F"That is an absolutely shocking
OL,9,Ffigure. There are so many women who
OL,10,Fare lucky to be with us today that
OL,11,Fthey could have been sadly another
OL,12,Fstatistic. Here is Northern Ireland
OL,13,Fhaving lost their life."
OL,15,FPatricia Reid feels she is one of the
OL,16,Flucky ones.
OL,18,FMarried for almost 20 years - her
OL,19,Fhusband tried to burn their house down
OL,20,Fin Co Down back in September 2021 with
OL,21,Fher in it.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
