PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1775913059
OL,3,C'He wanted to finish me off. All I
OL,4,Cever wanted to do was love him' -
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FIn her first television interview,
OL,8,FPatricia told us: "He hated me. He
OL,9,Fwanted to finish me off. All I ever
OL,10,Fwanted to do was love him.
OL,12,F"He was like something possessed. He
OL,13,Fnever spoke to me when I pleaded with
OL,14,Fhim 'please stop, please stop'.
OL,16,F"It was the worst I ever experienced
OL,17,Fin my life of terror, panic."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/4
