OL,3,C'He wanted to finish me off. All I
OL,4,Cever wanted to do was love him' -
OL,5,Csurvivor
OL,7,FPatricia's husband Michael McColl is
OL,8,Fnow in prison after admitting arson
OL,9,Fendangering life and was handed a
OL,10,Fseven-year sentence.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
